:100%;"&gt;&lt;b style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"&gt;How Can I Recover My Files? &lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:100%;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:100%;"  &gt;You can &lt;a href="http://www.stellarinfo.com/file-recovery.htm"&gt;recover deleted files&lt;/a&gt; using Stellar Phoenix file recovery software. This software uses powerful scanning mechanism to scan and preview the recoverable file which can be recovered by the software. It can recover deleted partitions of NTFS, FAT, HFS file system and different type of trashed MS Office Files, media files, Emails etc. It supports all the major versions of Windows and Mac OS.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:100%;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:100%;"  &gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:100%;"  &gt;To recover your deleted files, you need to follow the below mentioned steps:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:100%;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:100%;"  &gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;ul  style="text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:arial;"&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:100%;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://download.stellarinfo.com/stellar/StellarPhoenixWindowsFileRecovery.exe"&gt;Download for Windows&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href="http://download.stellarinfo.com/stellar/StellarPhoenixMacFileRecovery.dmg.zip"&gt;Download for MAC&lt;/a&gt; &amp;amp; install Stellar Phoenix File Recovery Software&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:100%;"&gt;Run the program&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:100%;"&gt;Click on 'Start Recovery' and a pop up window will appear to choose the desired drive where you think that the deleted data was stored.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:100%;"&gt;Click 'OK'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:100%;"&gt;This programs scan each sector and blocks and probably takes some time to shows you the heavily damaged file. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:100%;"&gt;After that, the software will shows the list of documents can be recovered by using this software on the right pane&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:100%;"&gt;You can buy the premium version of this software to fully recover the data because in the free version, you will only see the preview of recoverable files. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:100%;"  &gt;Including File Data Recovery software, you will get some bonus advantages with this software such as:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;ul  style="text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:arial;"&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:100%;"&gt;You can create image of the entire hard disk or a part of it. These created images can be used in case of data loss or partitions inaccessibility.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:100%;"&gt;This software comes with a bootable disc separately for MAC &amp;amp; Windows which will help you if your system fails to start.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div  style="text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:arial;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:100%;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:100%;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/4453101382727517102-7821901859899303737?l=datarecoverymethods.blogspot.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="h